     e. compatible b is open via double AllOpenSubspaceOpen
     f. Equivalence (fst X → Bool) ≃ Σ (fst S → Bool) compatible
        via rec→Set for backward map, PT.elim for section/retraction
     g. Σ-isODisc via OdiscSigma + PropOpenIffOdisc
